  - Title: The Imitation of Christ
    Location: I xxiv
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=No Helping Friend That Day
  - 239
  - 99
---
Suppose that thou hadst up to this day lived always in honours and
delights, what would it all avail thee if thou wert doomed to die at
this instant?

All therefore is vanity, except to love God and serve Him only.
